data.description:
This property boasts several notable features that contribute to its desirability as a residence. The primary bedroom is spacious and includes an en suite bathroom, along with custom shelves in the walk-in closet, providing ample storage space. The kitchen is well-equipped for entertaining, with granite countertops, new stainless-steel appliances, attractive lighting fixtures, and a large butcher block island, facilitating both meal preparation and socializing.
Outside, the property offers an oversized backyard, newly fenced for privacy and security, suitable for various uses such as entertaining guests or providing a safe area for pets. Additionally, the outdoor space features a large wood deck and a fire pit, ideal for enjoying evenings outdoors.
The home has undergone extensive remodeling and updates, ensuring that it is move-in ready for prospective buyers. Notable improvements include a new gas line for the dryer, custom shelves in the laundry room, custom blinds, and numerous other renovations aimed at enhancing the comfort and functionality of the property.
